{
  "stem": "14251.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was-- if you're two years old-- you know, I sat at the door at age two at my grandmother's before she died and cried till my parents came back.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And at that age, you just do what some have-- it's explained, it's adequate.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You're neither happy nor sad, neither one.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I remember Hilde took me on the streetcar to get to some other place.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember she sat down and I said, Tante Hilde, how come you're sitting down?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We're not allowed to sit down on the streetcar.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, there were rituals that we had done that we took for granted because we had to do them because of who we were that now were lifted by my being with another person, and I'm noticing the difference.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she-- she said-- years later, she said, do you remember that episode?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I said, oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because she was incapable of anger, this woman.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She was so kind and still is.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The onlookers in the streetcar clicked right here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "See, the Germans were trained to recognize and listen and observe and denounce everything they saw and heard, and even things they didn't see and hear.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She knew that some of the people on that streetcar knew what this meant.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She had to get off.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Immediately we had to get off.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And on a trip to the milk store-- in those times, each store was separate with what you needed pretty much-- I said, how come you're buying milk?",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We can't buy milk.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "See, this was dangerous stuff.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If my parent had been there, or one of them at least, I would have been told to keep my mouth closed and wouldn't be allowed to talk.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we had to leave the milk store very fast also.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
